Author: Florian Mounier aka paradoxxxzero
Description :
  This is an emacs major mode for pebble with:
       syntax highlighting
       sgml/html integration
       indentation (working with sgml)
       more to come

pebble-mode is based on jinja2-mode by Florian Mounier.
